{"id":278878,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/【首发】年初一群体事件：重庆千人围堵警车-江西/","date":"2013-02-12T04:30:55Z","modified":"2013-02-12T04:35:16Z","title":"【首发】年初一群体事件：重庆围堵警车 江西示威抗议污染 犯人越狱武警搜山","content":"<p><a name=\"more\"></a></p>\n<div><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">重庆警察徇私放走打人司机</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">千人围堵警车</span></b></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>2013</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">年</span><span>2</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">月</span><span>10</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">日大年初一下午</span><span>5</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">时，重庆市渝北区四号桥，一宝马车和</span><span>683</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">公交车发生争执，宝马司机狂打公交司机，交警接报赶到现场处理。</span><span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">宝马司机叫嚷他上面有人，随后交警接到一个上级打来的电话，就把宝马车放走了。</span><span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">据悉，打人者是交警中队某队长的亲属。</span><span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">警察公然徇私枉法，激起在场群众不满，其中一年轻女子拿起手机拍照，被警察抢走手机并被打，一名围观青年因在旁叫嚷被警察带到小巷殴打。</span><span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">事件引起公愤，群众开始起哄，逾千人包围警车讨说法，导致当地交通瘫痪。</span><span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">大批警察在场疏导群众但无效。</span><span>11</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">日凌晨，聚集人群自行散去。</span><span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-TQyxPddHvA0/URlZy00n3CI/AAAAAAAASv0/7ogvbEjPh90/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"476\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-TQyxPddHvA0/URlZy00n3CI/AAAAAAAASv0/7ogvbEjPh90/s640/1.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-H8ADIHYhdSs/URlZzAL-qdI/AAAAAAAASv4/AZpUihsap58/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"360\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-H8ADIHYhdSs/URlZzAL-qdI/AAAAAAAASv4/AZpUihsap58/s640/2.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-rGf1ioccor8/URlZz_M4iII/AAAAAAAASwE/vI9PZCLo5xY/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"360\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-rGf1ioccor8/URlZz_M4iII/AAAAAAAASwE/vI9PZCLo5xY/s640/3.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-8cbv95kSDos/URlZ1k7ir1I/AAAAAAAASwM/xoMx5EVb8vM/s1600/5.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-8cbv95kSDos/URlZ1k7ir1I/AAAAAAAASwM/xoMx5EVb8vM/s640/5.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-vOsyX9Y96Vg/URlZ2pIAnfI/AAAAAAAASwU/qCZCdslAKRc/s1600/6.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"478\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-vOsyX9Y96Vg/URlZ2pIAnfI/AAAAAAAASwU/qCZCdslAKRc/s640/6.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-4N8ishLXwwY/URlZ3yaQlPI/AAAAAAAASwc/tghGfUIgKZI/s1600/7.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-4N8ishLXwwY/URlZ3yaQlPI/AAAAAAAASwc/tghGfUIgKZI/s640/7.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-fHGu1dT5mfY/URlZ49kMaaI/AAAAAAAASwk/JSFy3u_tWm0/s1600/8.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"478\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-fHGu1dT5mfY/URlZ49kMaaI/AAAAAAAASwk/JSFy3u_tWm0/s640/8.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-rQEGY8RCFbE/URlZ51lP_gI/AAAAAAAASws/4Xsc-59EYLI/s1600/9.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"476\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-rQEGY8RCFbE/URlZ51lP_gI/AAAAAAAASws/4Xsc-59EYLI/s640/9.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-JJ2hJq-UGKY/URlZ7QCv2FI/AAAAAAAASw0/QyOgGlUd3os/s1600/10.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-JJ2hJq-UGKY/URlZ7QCv2FI/AAAAAAAASw0/QyOgGlUd3os/s640/10.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-SH7ipDWqaXI/URlZ8I5XDtI/AAAAAAAASw4/tG5g2QKHYIE/s1600/11.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"381\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-SH7ipDWqaXI/URlZ8I5XDtI/AAAAAAAASw4/tG5g2QKHYIE/s640/11.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-vOuWVpCkxT0/URlZ9Q61ucI/AAAAAAAASxE/DkYis49oF4A/s1600/12.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"482\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-vOuWVpCkxT0/URlZ9Q61ucI/AAAAAAAASxE/DkYis49oF4A/s640/12.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-s2oH6WdjAIc/URlatDCPZEI/AAAAAAAASyE/T8i8Xi2G5So/s1600/13A.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-s2oH6WdjAIc/URlatDCPZEI/AAAAAAAASyE/T8i8Xi2G5So/s1600/13A.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-qt81Xxv1UQA/URlZ_Po0AHI/AAAAAAAASxU/heXUs03pmK8/s1600/14.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"640\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-qt81Xxv1UQA/URlZ_Po0AHI/AAAAAAAASxU/heXUs03pmK8/s640/14.jpg\" width=\"480\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-dzTLsEApFrE/URlaAlp1JTI/AAAAAAAASxc/bzCbSd3C8yU/s1600/15.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-dzTLsEApFrE/URlaAlp1JTI/AAAAAAAASxc/bzCbSd3C8yU/s640/15.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-hK-WMYCKSLw/URlaBkl48hI/AAAAAAAASxk/YD31UYHBf9I/s1600/16a.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-hK-WMYCKSLw/URlaBkl48hI/AAAAAAAASxk/YD31UYHBf9I/s1600/16a.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-G7XMkoFzYNE/URlaCz-k1BI/AAAAAAAASxs/o8hq6MRhi10/s1600/18.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-G7XMkoFzYNE/URlaCz-k1BI/AAAAAAAASxs/o8hq6MRhi10/s1600/18.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<p> <b><span lang=\"EN-US\">江西上饶千人示威抗议工厂排污</span></b></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>2013</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">年</span><span>2</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">月</span><span>10</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">日年初一，江西上饶市玉山县下镇镇双元村，近千村民示威抗议工厂排污，导致生活环境被严重污染。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">村民</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">高喊“还我绿色，我要生存”，在厂区示威讨说法。</span><span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">村民</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">表示，当地政府被工厂老板收买，对环境污染不闻不问，包庇工厂隐瞒事实。村民多番投诉和抗议，厂方竟然叫来黑道威胁老百姓。</span><span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-U8mJ-K9oA9U/URlaEG_WhmI/AAAAAAAASx0/RGvLQDsACmU/s1600/28.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-U8mJ-K9oA9U/URlaEG_WhmI/AAAAAAAASx0/RGvLQDsACmU/s1600/28.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">网传南方集体越狱</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">八千武警镇压杀</span></b><b><span>35</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\">人</span></b><b><span></span></b></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">有网友在年初一爆料，近日一南方监狱出现史无前例的漏洞，导致大量犯人集体越狱，政府出动</span><span>8</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">千武警血腥镇压，当场击毙</span><span>35</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">人，武警亦有</span><span>81</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">人受伤。</span><span>5</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">人成功越狱，武警正全力追捕，事态仍在进展中。</span><span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">网友只上传一张大批武警持冲锋枪搜山的照片，没有其它图片，亦没有说明事发确实地点和时间。</span><span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-BDJkL_Rf5eo/URlaKr0on5I/AAAAAAAASx8/K7YXvIZzs8w/s1600/29.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-BDJkL_Rf5eo/URlaKr0on5I/AAAAAAAASx8/K7YXvIZzs8w/s1600/29.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<div><span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">中国茉莉花革命</span><span>http://www.molihua.org  </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">转载请注明出处</span><span></span></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":1002,"categories":[18269,10466],"tags":[22240,22247,22241,22245,22242,22246,19955,22244,22239,15021,22238,22243]}